trans-unit.source: Represents a class member, such as a property or event.
trans-unit.target: Representerer et klassen medlem, for eksempel en egenskap eller hendelse.

trans-unit.source: This is an abstract base class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en abstrakt basisklasse.

trans-unit.source: MemberDescriptor is the base class for the <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor> and the <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> classes.
trans-unit.target: MemberDescriptor er basisklasse for den <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>klasser.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> </xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor> class provides a description of an event, and the <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> class provides a description of a property.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>klassen inneholder en beskrivelse av en hendelse, og <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>klassen inneholder en beskrivelse av en egenskap.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> </xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: This class defines properties and methods to access its stored attributes.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen definerer egenskaper og metoder for å få tilgang til lagrede attributtene.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Attributes%2A> property gets the collection of attributes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Attributes%2A>egenskapen henter samlingen av attributter.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Attributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Category%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.IsBrowsable%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Description%2A>, and <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.DesignTimeOnly%2A> properties retrieve the values of those specific attributes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Category%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.IsBrowsable%2A>, <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Description%2A>, og <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.DesignTimeOnly%2A>Egenskaper hente verdiene for de bestemte attributtene.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.DesignTimeOnly%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Description%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.IsBrowsable%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Category%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Name%2A> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.DisplayName%2A> properties provide the name of the member.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Name%2A>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.DisplayName%2A>Egenskaper inneholder navnet på medlemmet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.DisplayName%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Name%2A>

trans-unit.source: The MemberDescriptor also defines an <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Equals%2A> method to compare this MemberDescriptor to another.
trans-unit.target: MemberDescriptor definerer også en <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Equals%2A>metode til å sammenligne denne MemberDescriptor til en annen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Equals%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Typically, you inherit from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor> and <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> classes, and not from this class.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Vanligvis du arve fra den <xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>og <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor>klasser, og ikke fra denne klassen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyDescriptor> </xref:System.ComponentModel.EventDescriptor>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> class with the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> klassen med den angitte <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> that contains the name of the member and its attributes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> som inneholder navnet på medlemmet og attributtene.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> class with the specified name of the member.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> klassen med det angitte navnet for medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: The name of the member.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: The name is an empty string ("") or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Navnet er en tom streng ("") eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> class with the name in the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> and the attributes in both the old <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> and the <xref:System.Attribute> array.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> klassen med navn i den angitte <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> og attributter i både gamle <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> og <xref:System.Attribute>matrise.</xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: This constructor appends the attributes in the <xref:System.Attribute> array to the attributes in the old <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor>.
trans-unit.target: Denne konstruktøren tilføyer attributtene i <xref:System.Attribute>matrisen slik at attributtene i gammelt <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor> </xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> that has the name of the member and its attributes.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> som er navnet på medlemmet og attributtene.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Attribute> objects with the attributes you want to add to the member.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Attribute>objekter med attributter du vil legge til medlemmet.</xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"></xref> class with the specified name of the member and an array of attributes.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor"> </xref> klassen med det angitte navnet for medlemmet og en matrise med attributter.

trans-unit.source: The name of the member.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref:System.Attribute> that contains the member attributes.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av typen <xref:System.Attribute>som inneholder medlemsattributter.</xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: The name is an empty string ("") or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Navnet er en tom streng ("") eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets an array of attributes.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en matrise med attributter.

trans-unit.source: Accessing this member allows derived classes to modify the default set of attributes that are used in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.CreateAttributeCollection%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Tilgang til dette medlemmet tillater avledede klasser endre standardsettet med attributter som brukes i den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.CreateAttributeCollection%2A>metoden.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.CreateAttributeCollection%2A>

trans-unit.source: An array of type <xref:System.Attribute> that contains the attributes of this member.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av typen <xref:System.Attribute>som inneholder attributter for dette medlemmet.</xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of attributes for this member.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av attributter for dette medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection> for this member, this property calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.CreateAttributeCollection%2A> method to create a new <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection> using the array of <xref:System.Attribute> objects passed to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection>for dette medlemmet egenskapen kaller den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.CreateAttributeCollection%2A>metode for å opprette en ny <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection>ved hjelp av en rekke <xref:System.Attribute>objekter som er sendt til konstruktøren.</xref:System.Attribute> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.CreateAttributeCollection%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection"></xref> that provides the attributes for this member, or an empty collection if there are no attributes in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray*>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection"> </xref> som inneholder attributtene for dette medlemmet, eller en tom samling hvis det finnes ingen attributter i <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray*>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the category to which the member belongs, as specified in the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.CategoryAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på kategorien medlemmet tilhører, som angitt i den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.CategoryAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A visual designer can use this property value to display members in categories.
trans-unit.target: Visuelle utformeren kan bruke denne egenskapsverdien til å vise medlemmer i kategorier.

trans-unit.source: The name of the category to which the member belongs.
trans-unit.target: Navnet på kategorien medlemmet tilhører.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref href="System.ComponentModel.CategoryAttribute"></xref>, the category name is set to the default category, <xref uid="langword_csharp_Misc" name="Misc" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen <xref href="System.ComponentModel.CategoryAttribute"> </xref>, kategorinavnet er satt til standardkategorien <xref uid="langword_csharp_Misc" name="Misc" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a collection of attributes using the array of attributes passed to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en samling av attributtene ved hjelp av en rekke attributter som er sendt til konstruktøren.

trans-unit.source: This method is called from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Attributes%2A> property when there is no <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection> for this member.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kalles fra den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Attributes%2A>når det er ingen <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection>for dette medlemmet.</xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.Attributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: If there are no attributes in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray%2A>, this will return an empty <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det finnes ingen attributter i <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray%2A>dette returnerer et tomt <xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray%2A>

trans-unit.source: A new <xref href="System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection"></xref> that contains the <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray*> attributes.
trans-unit.target: En ny <xref href="System.ComponentModel.AttributeCollection"> </xref> som inneholder den <xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray*>attributter.</xref:System.ComponentModel.MemberDescriptor.AttributeArray*>

trans-unit.source: Gets the description of the member, as specified in the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DescriptionAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter beskrivelsen av medlemmet som er angitt i den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DescriptionAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A visual designer can use this description to display information about this member.
trans-unit.target: Visuelle utformeren kan bruke denne beskrivelsen for å vise informasjon om dette medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: The description of the member.
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelsen av medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DescriptionAttribute"></xref>, the property value is set to the default, which is an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DescriptionAttribute"> </xref>, egenskapsverdien er satt til standard, som er en tom streng ("").

trans-unit.source: Gets whether this member should be set only at design time, as specified in the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignOnlyAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter om dette medlemmet kan bare angis under utformingen, som er angitt i den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignOnlyAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: If there is no <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignOnlyAttribute>, the return value is the default, which is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er ingen <xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignOnlyAttribute>, er returverdien standardinnstillingen, som er `false`.</xref:System.ComponentModel.DesignOnlyAttribute>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if this member should be set only at design time; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the member can be set during run time.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis dette medlemmet kan bare angis på forhånd. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> hvis Medlemmet kan angis under kjøring.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name that can be displayed in a window, such as a Properties window.
trans-unit.target: Henter navnet som kan vises i et vindu, for eksempel en Egenskaper-vinduet.

trans-unit.source: The name to display for the member.
trans-unit.target: Navnet som skal vises for medlemmet.

trans-unit.source: Compares this instance to the given object to see if they are equivalent.
trans-unit.target: Sammenligner denne forekomsten til det angitte objektet til å se om de er like.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare to the current instance.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å sammenligne den gjeldende forekomsten.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if equivalent; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis tilsvarende; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, adds the attributes of the inheriting class to the specified list of attributes in the parent class.
trans-unit.target: Når overstyrt i en avledet klasse, legger du til attributtene for arvede klassen til den angitte listen over attributter i den overordnede klassen.

trans-unit.source: For duplicate attributes, the last one added to the list is kept.
trans-unit.target: Den siste som legges til i listen er beholdt for dupliserte attributter.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Collections.IList> with the attributes is created once.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Collections.IList>med attributtene opprettes én gang.</xref:System.Collections.IList>

trans-unit.source: If there are duplicate attributes in the list, only the first instance is saved; all subsequent duplicate attributes are removed from the list.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det er dupliserte attributter i listen, lagres bare den første forekomsten. alle etterfølgende dupliserte attributter er fjernet fra listen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Collections.IList> that lists the attributes in the parent class.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.IList>som viser attributtene i den overordnede klasse.</xref:System.Collections.IList>

trans-unit.source: Initially, this is empty.
trans-unit.target: Dette er første gang, tom.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the object that should be used during invocation of members.
trans-unit.target: Henter objektet som skal brukes under aktivering av medlemmer.

trans-unit.source: Normally, the return value will be the same as the `instance` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis returverdien skal være den samme som den `instance` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: If another object has been associated with this instance, or if the instance is a custom type descriptor, the GetInvocationTarget method may return a different value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis et annet objekt er knyttet til denne forekomsten, eller hvis forekomsten er en egendefinert typebeskrivelse, metoden GetInvocationTarget kan returnere en annen verdi.
